metadata.name: ELITE #1
metadata.description:
Colizeum ELITE is a collection of 5000 unique characters. Each one of ELITES NFTs is a factory capable of minting NFT assets and Colizeum Gold tokens. Together as a whole, they own and govern the economy of the Colizeum.
Use ELITE NFT to play Colizeum Games, mint your personal network of players and earn.
https://www.colizeum.com
